"title": "7478: washing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7478",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The physical or ritual cleansing of part or all of a person's body, a person's clothing or certain vessels. Washing can be symbolic of purification from defilement or cleansing from sin. It can also be part of preparation for a special act of religious service.</p>\n<h2>Washing as the cleansing of the body, clothing or certain vessels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:17-Exod30:21\">EXO 30:17–30:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:53-Lev13:54\">LEV 13:53–13:54</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:30-Exod40:32\">EXO 40:30–40:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:27\">LEV 6:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:8-Lev14:9\">LEV 14:8–14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:2-Lev15:13\">LEV 15:2–15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:24\">LEV 16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:26-Lev16:28\">LEV 16:26–16:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:24\">NUM 31:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:6\">2CH 4:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:38\">1KI 7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:6\">JHN 2:6</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ taught that inner purity was more important than ritual washing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:17-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:17–15:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:20-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:20–7:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:1-Mark7:9\">MRK 7:1–7:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:3\">MAT 15:1–15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:14-Mark7:15\">MRK 7:14–7:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:10-Matt15:11\">MAT 15:10–15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:37-Luke11:41\">LUK 11:37–11:41</a></p>\n<h2>Washing as a symbolic act</h2>\n<h3>Of purification from defilement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:24-Lev11:25\">LEV 11:24–11:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:28\">LEV 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:40\">LEV 11:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:6\">LEV 13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:34\">LEV 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:4-Lev15:8\">LEV 15:4–15:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:15-Lev17:16\">LEV 17:15–17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:10-Deut23:11\">DEU 23:10–23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:10\">2KI 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>Of cleansing from sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:9–6:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:25–5:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:2\">PSA 51:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:7\">PSA 51:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:16\">ISA 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:4\">ISA 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:14\">JER 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:16\">ACT 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5\">TIT 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:14\">REV 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></p>\n<h3>Of personal cleansing before a special act of religious service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:24\">LEV 16:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:10-Exod19:11\">EXO 19:10–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:4\">EXO 29:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:12-Exod40:13\">EXO 40:12–40:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:30-Exod40:32\">EXO 40:30–40:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:6\">LEV 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:6-Num8:7\">NUM 8:6–8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:21\">NUM 8:21</a></p>\n<h3>Washing one's hands was used as a symbolic declaration of innocence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:6-Deut21:7\">DEU 21:6–21:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:6\">PSA 26:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:13\">PSA 73:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:24\">MAT 27:24</a></p>",
